title: Wheatbelt road safety report 'likely' to spark renewed education campaign in bid to cut road toll
text: Road safety commissioner Kim Papalia says a report on how to tackle the high fatality rate on Wheatbelt roads in Western Australia is likely to be handed down by the end of the year. ...
